+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01T5whQe7YMzjMbqXkAxeehn","type":"tool_result","content":"     1â†’# T9: SSG Toolkit\n     2â†’\n     3â†’Add 8 plugins to an existing Static Site Generator toolkit.\n     4â†’\n     5â†’## Starting State\n     6â†’- `src/core/` contains the build engine, types, and templates (~600 lines)\n     7â†’- 15 existing tests in `tests/core.test.ts` â€” these must continue to pass\n     8â†’- Plugin test files in `tests/plugins/` define the expected behavior\n     9â†’\n    10â†’## Requirements\n    11â†’\n    12â†’Build 8 plugins in `src/plugins/`, each implementing the `Plugin` interface from `src/core/types.ts`.\n    13â†’\n    14â†’### Wave 1 (no dependencies)\n    15â†’1. **markdown-ext** â€” Markdown â†’ HTML with footnotes and admonition containers\n    16â†’2. **asset-pipeline** â€” Rewrite asset URLs and generate manifest\n    17â†’3. **syntax-highlight** â€” Add language classes to code blocks\n    18â†’4. **taxonomy** â€” Build tag/category indices and generate tag pages\n    19â†’\n    20â†’### Wave 2 (depend on Wave 1)\n    21â†’5. **rss-feed** â€” Generate RSS 2.0 feed (depends: markdown-ext, taxonomy)\n    22â†’6. **search-index** â€” Generate search index JSON (depends: markdown-ext, syntax-highlight)\n    23â†’\n    24â†’### Wave 3 (depend on Wave 2)\n    25â†’7. **sitemap** â€” Generate sitemap XML (depends: taxonomy, rss-feed)\n    26â†’8. **dev-server** â€” Generate dev server config (depends: asset-pipeline, search-index)\n    27â†’\n    28â†’### Plugin Interface\n    29â†’Each plugin must export a `createXxxPlugin()` factory function that returns a `Plugin` object.\n    30â†’\n    31â†’## Validation\n    32â†’- `npm test` â€” all tests must pass (15 existing + 60 new)\n    33â†’- `npm run build` â€” must compile\n    34â†’- `npm run lint` â€” must be clean\n    35â†’"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_018Hc4Y1Kgka332QBPt6Hy6j","session_id":"f8feecf4-a0c5-4c57-9f40-722e41d8ebb2","uui